{"tid":2219133,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"20 人闖港大毀連儂牆　與學生對罵","createTime":"2020-09-26T16:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T03:01:03.000Z","uid":281029,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"315a31420cf87ec72ed7ab471d9cd3ac1b72a05d","tid":2219133,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T16:24:31.000Z","msg":"【】<br />\n<br />\n港大學生會學苑即時新聞報道，今（26 日）有約 20 名身份不明人士闖入校園，撕毀位於大學街上層的 3 幅連儂牆，並推倒港大學生會旗幟。<br />\n<br />\n港大學生會表示，事發在今晚約 7 時，附上一段由同學拍攝的片段。片中可見撕文宣的人與學生對罵，有人大呼粗口；有人自稱「清理香港啲垃圾」及「清潔香港」。同場有多名大學保安勸諭相關人士離開，眾人之後離開港大範圍。<br />\n<br />\n港大學生會表示，正研究下一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n另見報道：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3i2hHet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3i2hHet&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0pE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=f4a68ff2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3i2hHet</a><br />\n<br />\n影片來源：香港大學學生會<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3i2hHet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3i2hHet&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0pE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=f4a68ff2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3i2hHet</a>"},{"pid":"2e8c4b4e090e9f3664538d6c8c056ff55fb17b93","tid":2219133,"uid":372131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T16:42:05.000Z","msg":"唔使勞煩佢哋出手啦 XGU班奶共高層自己都會做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6d7c024a68b5997decbe01ae94719137fdd386","tid":2219133,"uid":81657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:36:03.000Z","msg":"你睇啲實蕉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f0702d7bd295512d87ff7c44e3e485e1edd15d7","tid":2219133,"uid":340088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:38:27.000Z","msg":"廢老"},{"pid":"10257f8a587c224a30099a7452e75fb703353054","tid":2219133,"uid":364850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T03:01:03.000Z","msg":"廢老:字都唔識多隻終於可以入港大<img src=\"/asse